    "name": "Dark Queen of Samobor",
    "steam_appid": 3106050,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106050/extras/ad4c7e468c78da8ef2d4d1086d8d4a41.avif?t=1761580437\" width=600 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106050/extras/17a6c29c4af5efa5dfe633a4fd2411ed.poster.avif?t=1761580437\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106050/extras/17a6c29c4af5efa5dfe633a4fd2411ed.webm?t=1761580437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106050/extras/17a6c29c4af5efa5dfe633a4fd2411ed.mp4?t=1761580437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在这个2.5D动作冒险类游戏中，开始一段受斯拉夫神话和克罗地亚民俗启发的旅程，灵感来自《Inside》、《Neva》和《Song of Iron》等。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过这个游戏，我们希望让你回想起小时候听到的那些英雄故事，就像是走进一本奇幻书籍，你将扮演一个中世纪的骑士，从十字军东征的艰苦战斗中归来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，没有时间休息，你的家园正笼罩在邪恶女王编织的黑暗之中。在魔法森林到荒凉废土的各种场景中，与怪物以及史诗首领殊死搏杀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >下一个灌木丛后面会潜伏着的什么? 你会遇到什么样的怪物? 你甚至还没有为这场惨烈的战斗做好准备-但如果你打算生存下去，你将不得不提高自己的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106050/extras/d2e37ee0f2ac8d07aa41eff4e2de2a57.avif?t=1761580437\" width=600 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106050/extras/98a016f2fd6f7e60eb147de49c4c0765.poster.avif?t=1761580437\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106050/extras/98a016f2fd6f7e60eb147de49c4c0765.webm?t=1761580437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106050/extras/98a016f2fd6f7e60eb147de49c4c0765.mp4?t=1761580437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106050/extras/6410686dec48dd150606d29bcb102203.avif?t=1761580437\" width=600 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106050/extras/572e4931e77be58573c49f91351a5714.poster.avif?t=1761580437\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106050/extras/572e4931e77be58573c49f91351a5714.webm?t=1761580437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106050/extras/572e4931e77be58573c49f91351a5714.mp4?t=1761580437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106050/extras/a6b1ce290015762ce24a385afe6c9847.avif?t=1761580437\" width=600 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106050/extras/90b5af6734f9b3b1e672d8c61072419d.poster.avif?t=1761580437\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106050/extras/90b5af673